<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>Mesa de Trabajo ✦</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#182026;--ink2:#34424b;--dim:#75808a;
  --bg:#f6f4ef;--bg2:#ece7dc;--bg3:#ded7c8;--w:#ffffff;
  --blue:#346b80;--blue-d:#244c5d;--blue-l:#e6f1f4;--blue-m:#91bdc8;
  --olive:#6d7f46;--olive-d:#4e5e31;--olive-l:#edf2e2;--olive-m:#b8c991;
  --clay:#b56b4d;--clay-d:#8d4a30;--clay-l:#f5e8e0;--clay-m:#d59b83;
  --gold:#b58a35;--gold-d:#7d5c1e;--gold-l:#f6edd8;--gold-m:#d8bd78;
  --rose:#a85c71;--rose-d:#7d3f53;--rose-l:#f4e6ea;
  --bdr:#d8cec0;--bdr2:#c6b9a8;--r:12px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html,body{height:100%;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg3);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--ink);font-size:14px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:300}
button,input,textarea,select{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}
button{cursor:pointer}
.app{height:100dvh;display:grid;grid-template-rows:54px 1fr;overflow:hidden}
.topbar{background:var(--ink);color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:0 18px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);z-index:10}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:17px;color:#fff8ee;white-space:nowrap}
.brand .star{color:var(--gold-m);font-size:18px}.brand small{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-left:2px}.top-actions{margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center}.search{width:260px;max-width:32vw;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 13px;color:white;font-size:12px}.search::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.userchip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:999px;padding:4px 12px 4px 4px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.avatar{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue-l);color:var(--blue-d);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:11px}
.body{display:grid;grid-template-columns:230px 1fr;height:100%;overflow:hidden}.sidebar{background:var(--bg2);border-right:1px solid var(--bdr);display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}.side-head{padding:18px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bdr)}.side-ey{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);font-weight:700}.side-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:25px;line-height:1;color:var(--blue-d);margin:4px 0}.side-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5}.nav{padding:9px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1}.navitem{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 10px;border-radius:10px;color:var(--ink2);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:2px;border:1px solid transparent;transition:.12s}.navitem:hover{background:white;border-color:var(--bdr)}.navitem.active{background:var(--blue-l);border-color:var(--blue-m);color:var(--blue-d);font-weight:600}.navitem span{width:20px;text-align:center;font-size:16px}.badge{margin-left:auto;background:var(--clay);color:white;font-size:10px;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:999px}.side-foot{padding:10px;border-top:1px solid var(--bdr)}.pulse{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:11px}.pulse-title{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);font-weight:700}.pulse-main{display:flex;align-items:end;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:5px}.pulse-n{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:29px;color:var(--blue-d);line-height:1}.pulse-l{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim)}.bar{height:4px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:8px}.barf{height:100%;background:var(--blue);border-radius:999px;width:0%}
.main{background:var(--bg);overflow-y:auto}.sec{display:none;padding:24px 30px;max-width:1180px}.sec.active{display:block}.sec-hd{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;margin-bottom:18px}.sec-hd h2{font-size:27px;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:3px}.sec-hd p{font-size:13px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5}.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:8px 13px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;transition:.15s}.btn-primary{background:var(--blue);color:white}.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--blue-d)}.btn-clay{background:var(--clay);color:white}.btn-outline{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);color:var(--ink2)}.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--bdr2)}.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--dim);padding:5px 8px}.btn-sm{padding:5px 9px;font-size:11px}
.grid{display:grid;gap:12px}.grid2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.grid3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.grid4{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}.card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:14px;padding:15px 17px}.card-title{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}.hero{background:var(--ink);border-radius:18px;padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:16px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:20px;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.hero:before{content:'';position:absolute;width:340px;height:340px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);opacity:.09;top:-120px;right:-80px}.hero:after{content:'';position:absolute;width:220px;height:220px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);opacity:.07;bottom:-90px;left:35%}.hero>*{position:relative}.ey{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold-m);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:7px}.hero h1{font-size:32px;color:#fff8ee;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:5px}.hero p{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.46);line-height:1.6;max-width:620px}.datebox{text-align:right}.datebox .day{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:48px;color:var(--gold-m);line-height:1}.datebox .label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.stat{background:var(--bg);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px}.stat .n{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:28px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1}.stat .l{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:3px}.mini-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}.mini-item{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}.mini-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}.dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;margin-top:6px;flex-shrink:0}.dot.alta{background:var(--clay)}.dot.media{background:var(--gold)}.dot.baja{background:var(--olive)}.mini-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}.mini-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:1px}.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;border-radius:999px;padding:2px 7px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700}.tag-blue{background:var(--blue-l);color:var(--blue-d)}.tag-olive{background:var(--olive-l);color:var(--olive-d)}.tag-clay{background:var(--clay-l);color:var(--clay-d)}.tag-gold{background:var(--gold-l);color:var(--gold-d)}.tag-rose{background:var(--rose-l);color:var(--rose-d)}
.filters{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px}.pill{padding:5px 11px;background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:999px;font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);font-weight:700}.pill.active{background:var(--blue-l);border-color:var(--blue-m);color:var(--blue-d)}.project-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:12px}.project-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:15px;padding:16px;transition:.15s}.project-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}.project-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start}.project-name{font-size:17px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.15}.project-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.6;margin:8px 0 12px}.progress-line{height:5px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden}.progress-line div{height:100%;background:var(--blue);border-radius:999px}.project-foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:9px;font-size:11px;color:var(--dim)}
.task{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-left:4px solid transparent;border-radius:13px;padding:13px 14px;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;gap:10px}.task.alta{border-left-color:var(--clay)}.task.media{border-left-color:var(--gold)}.task.baja{border-left-color:var(--olive)}.check{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--bdr);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}.check.done{background:var(--olive);border-color:var(--olive);color:white}.check.done:after{content:'✓';font-size:11px}.task-body{flex:1;min-width:0}.task-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:3px}.task-title.done{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--dim)}.task-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:7px}.task-meta{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}.task-actions{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-shrink:0}.week{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:10px}.daycol{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:14px;min-height:320px;overflow:hidden}.dayhd{background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bdr);padding:10px 12px}.dayname{font-weight:800;color:var(--ink2);font-size:13px}.daydate{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:1px}.daybody{padding:10px}.daytask{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:10px;padding:9px;margin-bottom:7px}.daytask b{font-size:12px}.daytask p{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.4;margin-top:2px}.meeting{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:13px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:9px}.meeting-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:7px}.meeting-title{font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);font-size:14px}.meeting-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim)}.meeting p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6}.note{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:13px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:9px}.note-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:7px}.note-kind{font-weight:800;font-size:11px;color:var(--blue-d)}.note-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--dim)}.note p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.7}.report-box{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:15px;padding:18px}.report-output{white-space:pre-wrap;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:14px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink2);min-height:260px}.formrow{margin-bottom:12px}.formrow label{display:block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:5px}.formrow input,.formrow textarea,.formrow select{width:100%;border:1px solid var(--bdr);background:var(--bg);border-radius:10px;padding:9px 11px;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink)}.formrow textarea{min-height:80px;resize:vertical;line-height:1.6}.formrow input:focus,.formrow textarea:focus,.formrow select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--blue-m);background:white}.modal-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(24,32,38,.52);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:18px;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(3px)}.modal-bg.on{display:flex}.modal{background:white;border-radius:16px;max-width:520px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto;padding:22px;box-shadow:0 20px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}.modal h3{font-size:21px;margin-bottom:14px}.actions{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;gap:8px;margin-top:15px}.empty{text-align:center;padding:34px 14px;color:var(--dim)}.empty .ico{font-size:34px;opacity:.3;margin-bottom:8px}.access-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}.access-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}.access-name{font-weight:800}.access-mail{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:1px}.toast{position:fixed;right:18px;bottom:18px;background:var(--ink);color:white;border-radius:11px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;z-index:200;transform:translateY(50px);opacity:0;transition:.25s}.toast.show{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}
@media(max-width:900px){.body{grid-template-columns:1fr}.sidebar{display:none}.top-actions .search{display:none}.sec{padding:16px}.grid2,.grid3,.grid4,.week{grid-template-columns:1fr}.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr}.datebox{text-align:left}.project-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.brand small{display:none}}

/* CASOS ESPECÍFICOS */
.case-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:12px}
.case-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:14px;padding:15px 16px;transition:.15s;border-left:4px solid var(--blue)}
.case-card:hover{border-color:var(--bdr2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.case-card.alerta-alta{border-left-color:var(--clay)}
.case-card.alerta-media{border-left-color:var(--gold)}
.case-card.alerta-baja{border-left-color:var(--olive)}
.case-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;margin-bottom:7px}
.case-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.3}
.case-type{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:2px}
.case-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.55;margin:8px 0}
.case-next{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:10px;padding:9px 10px;margin-top:9px}
.case-next b{display:block;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:3px}
.case-next span{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.5}
.case-meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:9px}
.case-history{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5;margin-top:8px;border-top:1px solid var(--bdr);padding-top:8px}


/* DETALLE DE PROYECTO */
.project-detail{display:none}
.project-detail.on{display:block}
.project-list-view.off{display:none}
.proj-hero{background:var(--ink);border-radius:18px;padding:20px 22px;margin-bottom:14px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;color:white}
.proj-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;width:260px;height:260px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);opacity:.18;right:-80px;top:-110px}
.proj-back{position:relative;z-index:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);padding:6px 12px;border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
.proj-back:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.16);color:white}
.proj-hero h2{position:relative;z-index:1;font-size:27px;color:white;margin-bottom:5px}
.proj-hero p{position:relative;z-index:1;color:rgba(255,255,255,.62);font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;max-width:720px}
.proj-hero-meta{position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:12px}
.proj-tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:4px;margin-bottom:14px;overflow-x:auto}
.proj-tab{border:none;background:transparent;color:var(--dim);padding:7px 12px;border-radius:9px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
.proj-tab.active{background:white;color:var(--blue-d);box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.proj-panel{display:none}
.proj-panel.active{display:block}
.proj-summary-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr .8fr;gap:12px}
.proj-kpis{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px}
.proj-kpi{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:11px 12px;text-align:center}
.proj-kpi .n{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:24px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1}
.proj-kpi .l{font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:3px}
.proj-empty{background:white;border:1px dashed var(--bdr);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;text-align:center;color:var(--dim);font-size:13px}
.proj-next-box{background:white;border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px}
.proj-next-box h4{font-size:14px;margin-bottom:7px;color:var(--ink)}
.proj-next-box p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6}
@media(max-width:800px){.proj-summary-grid,.proj-kpis{grid-template-columns:1fr}.proj-tabs{padding-bottom:5px}}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="brand"><span class="star">✦</span>Mesa de Trabajo <small>gestión académica y proyectos · v4 modal corregido</small></div>
    <div class="top-actions">
      <input class="search" id="globalSearch" placeholder="Buscar tareas, proyectos, notas…" oninput="renderAll()">
      <div class="userchip"><div class="avatar">FP</div><span>Fabián · Admin</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="side-head">
        <div class="side-ey">Centro de mando</div>
        <div class="side-title">Trabajo</div>
        <div class="side-sub">Prioridades, proyectos, reuniones y reportes en un solo lugar.</div>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav" id="nav">
        <div class="navitem active" onclick="navTo('inicio')"><span>🏠</span>Inicio</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('proyectos')"><span>📁</span>Proyectos</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('tareas')"><span>✅</span>Tareas <b class="badge" id="taskBadge">0</b></div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('semana')"><span>🗓️</span>Semana</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('casos')"><span>🎯</span>Casos específicos</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('reuniones')"><span>📝</span>Reuniones</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('bitacora')"><span>📓</span>Bitácora</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('reportes')"><span>📊</span>Reportes</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('acceso')"><span>👥</span>Acceso</div>
        <div class="navitem" onclick="navTo('ajustes')"><span>⚙️</span>Ajustes</div>
      </nav>
      <div class="side-foot">
        <div class="pulse">
          <div class="pulse-title">Pulso semanal</div>
          <div class="pulse-main"><div><div class="pulse-n" id="pulseDone">0%</div><div class="pulse-l">tareas cerradas</div></div><div class="pulse-l" id="pulseDate">—</div></div>
          <div class="bar"><div class="barf" id="pulseBar"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <main class="main">
      <section class="sec active" id="sec-inicio">
        <div class="hero">
          <div>
            <div class="ey">Prioridad de hoy</div>
            <h1>Qué mirar, qué cerrar y qué preparar.</h1>
            <p>Una portada ejecutiva para ordenar el trabajo académico, los proyectos UTE, las reuniones y los pendientes que no pueden perderse.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="datebox"><div class="day" id="todayDay">—</div><div class="label" id="todayLabel">hoy</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid4" style="margin-bottom:12px">
          <div class="stat"><div class="n" id="sPend">0</div><div class="l">pendientes</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="n" id="sUrg">0</div><div class="l">urgentes</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="n" id="sProj">0</div><div class="l">proyectos activos</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="n" id="sCases">0</div><div class="l">casos abiertos</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="n" id="sMeet">0</div><div class="l">reuniones próximas</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid2">
          <div class="card"><div class="card-title">🔥 Tareas urgentes</div><div id="inicioUrgentes" class="mini-list"></div></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-title">🗓️ Próximas reuniones</div><div id="inicioReuniones" class="mini-list"></div></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-title">📁 Proyectos activos</div><div id="inicioProyectos" class="mini-list"></div></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-title">📓 Últimas notas</div><div id="inicioNotas" class="mini-list"></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="sec" id="sec-proyectos">
        <div id="projectListView" class="project-list-view">
          <div class="sec-hd"><div><h2>Proyectos</h2><p>Cada línea de trabajo tiene tareas, hitos, responsables y próximos pasos.</p></div><button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openModal('project')">+ Proyecto</button></div>
